<li>UK GOVERNMENT., 2019. <em><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/salt-targets-2017-progress-report" title="Salt targets progress report">Salt Targets 2017: progress report</a> A report on the food industry’s progress towards meeting the 2017 salt targets. </em>[Online]. Public Health England. [Accessed 28 February 2022]. </li>
<li>UK GOVERNMENT., 2020. <em><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/salt-reduction-targets-for-2024" title="Salt reduction targets 2024">Salt Reduction Targets for 2024</a>. </em>[Online]. Public Health England. [Accessed 16 February 2022]. </li>
